{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"TIANCHENGHUODONG2","fadeType":1,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"side":2,"say":"I am Nagato, the flagship of the Combined Fleet! I will be the referee for this year's Naval Exercises!","bgm":"nagato-map","nameColor":"#a9f548","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...In these turbulent times, we face threats on all sides, not only from the chaos the Sirens are causing, but also from other forces around the world. And so...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... now more than ever, we must all come together as one!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And we must show our enemies that the Sakura Empire Fleet is stronger than it has ever been before!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"withoutActorName":true,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The flagship of the Combined Fleet and shrine maiden of the Sakura Empire, Nagato, gazed at all the ships in attendance for the wargames.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The flagship of the winning side of this year's wargames shall be appointed as the Combined Fleet's next flagship!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"actorName":"Audience","say":"!!!","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","dialogShake":{"number":2,"x":12.75,"speed":0.09},"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2},{"side":2,"say":"Nagato-sama's... next flagship?!","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305070},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Be quiet!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I will now announce the team compositions for this year's wargames!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Red Team: Battlecruiser Amagi...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Blue Team: Battleship Kaga...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305060},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh what a delight! Amagi, are you ready for that rematch?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305070},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"This year's wargames will decide the future course of events for our Combined Fleet.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I want everyone to bear this fact in mind. I want you to demonstrate what you are capable of and fight without remorse!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050},{"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"...Now, let the Combined Fleet's wargames begin!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305050}]}